1)autoSizeColumn(colKey) - Auto-sizes a column based on its contents.
2)autoSizeColumns(colKeys) - same as above but resizes more than one columns. paramater passed 
    is array of keys
3)getAllColumns() - Returns all the columns, regardless of visible or not.
4)getAllGridColumns() -Returns all the grid columns, same as getAllColumns(), except 
    a) it has the order of the columns that are presented in the grid and 
    b) it's after the 'pivot' step, so if pivoting, has the value columns for the pivot. 
5)
